                "invention-title": [
                    "Clean hydrogen production and energy supply system",
                    "一种清洁制氢及供能系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a clean hydrogen production and energy supply system. The output end of a photo-thermal system of the clean hydrogen production and energy supply system is connected with the input end of a heat storage system; the output end of the heat storage system is connected with the input end of the thermochemical hydrogen production system; and a gas outlet of the thermochemical hydrogen production system outputs hydrogen. Through combination of the photo-thermal system and the heat storage system, 24-hour continuous driving hydrogen production can be realized, the generated hydrogen can be supplied to hydrogen equipment for use, and the hydrogen production effect is remarkably improved; meanwhile, a new energy power generation system, a water electrolysis hydrogen production system, a steam turbine, a fuel cell, a hydrogen storage tank, an electric power supply system, a hydrogen refueling station and the like can be further included, so that hydrogen is comprehensively produced through multiple ways such as photovoltaics, wind power and heat energy, hydrogen can be continuously produced, and the yield can be increased; the new energy system is combined with the heat storage system and the hydrogen storage system, so that an electric power peak regulation absorption effect can be achieved, and stable supply of electric energy and hydrogen energy is realized; and in addition, the generated electric energy and hydrogen energy both come from solar energy and wind energy, are clean and environment-friendly, and have high economic benefits."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种清洁制氢及供能系统，其光热系统的输出端与储热系统的输入端相连；其储热系统的输出端与热化学制氢系统的输入端相连；热化学制氢系统的出气口输出氢气；从而通过光热系统与储热系统结合，可实现24小时连续驱动制氢，产生的氢气可以供给用氢设备使用，显著改善制氢效果；同时还可以包括新能源发电系统、电解水制氢系统、汽轮机、燃料电池、储氢罐、电力供应系统和加氢站等，从而使得通过光伏、风电和热能等多种途径综合制氢，即可连续制氢，又可提高产量；并且将新能源系统与储热系统、储氢系统相结合，可起到电力调峰消纳作用，并实现电能、氢能的稳定供应；另外产生的电能和氢能均来源于太阳能和风能，清洁环保，且经济效益高。"
                }
